description:
I have a 15 yr old son who lives with me, and 2 baby dogs who I love so much.

I love photography. I love traveling. I love food. 

We are too old to play, let’s get real! If you are here to just have “fun”, pls spare me. 

I’m not the prettiest but I’m someone who makes no drama. I just want to be happy with someone who will love me for who I am and I will love you him back a hundred folds...
